Package kodkod.core.bool

Interface Summary
BooleanVisitor<T,A> Visits boolean values.
 

Class Summary
AbstractBooleanVisitor<T,A> A skeletal implementation of the visitor interface.
BooleanConstant Represents a boolean constant, true or false.
BooleanFactory A factory for creating and assembling boolean values.
BooleanFormula Represents a non-constant boolean value.
BooleanMatrix Represents an n-dimensional matrix of boolean values.
BooleanValue Represents a boolean value, which may be a formula or a constant.
BooleanVariable Represents a boolean variable.
Dimensions Stores information about the size of a matrix.
MultiGate Represents a gate with two or more inputs; an AND or an OR gate.
MutableMultiGate Represents a mutable multi gate that allows incremental addition of inputs.
NotGate Represents a NOT gate.
 

Enum Summary
MultiGate.Operator Represents the operator used to combine the input variables of a MultiGate.
